01/05/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- Prime Minister Fatos Nano is proposing that the government honour US Secretary of State Colin Powell with the order of Gjergj Kastriot Skenderbeg, in recognition of his role "in support of the new democracies that share equal values with the United States". 
Powell will travel to Tirana Friday for the signing of US-Adriatic Charter by Albania, Croatia and Macedonia. 
(ATA - 30/04/03)
